PySpark code is deployed from GitLab repositories.
Processed data are exposed in partitioned delta lake or parquet directories.

div.p: Our organization runs Kubeflow as a Kubernetes-native analytics environment for Statisticians, Economists, and other data professionals.
These individuals maintain Reproducible Analytical Pipelines (RAPs)written in Python and R, using tools from the Open Source Python/R Data Science ecosystem.

div.p: A collection of data products is maintained that uses Machine Learning (ML) to predict which CPI categories consumer products belong to.
A custom quality assurance application is maintained to correct misclassified records.
